Present location: INSTITUT DE PAPYROLOGIE ET D'ÉGYPTOLOGIE, UNIVERSITÉ DE LILLE III [02/049] LILLE
Name: Model of a vase
Description: Model of a tubular vase with a slightly bulging body that is restricted in its upper section.It has a small, flat circular base that is quite irregular. There are several accumulations of clay on the body and the bottom and there is a slight depression at the mouth.See E27 031, 27 032, 27 033, 27 034, 27 035, 27 037.
